name: Document
description:
ABOUT ME
Document is a handmade handheld clutch bag, with a "document" icon printed all over the bag. Inside of the custom design prints, are upcycling old magazines. Plastic coated,featuring a contrast flap closure with 2 magnetic buttons and black metallic chain for holding.

Orange on the sideways, document icon on the inside and black seperator.

www.interactivemania.com
www.defaulticon.com

LOOK AFTER ME
Wipe clean with a damp cloth.

PRICE: 49.99€
PRODUCT CODE: Di004WB
